description: This file defines API prototypes for managing WiFi configuration data in a data model context. It includes function declarations for getting and setting string parameters related to LAN configuration within a WiFi management module.

methods.name: Lanconfig_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves the value of a specified string parameter related to LAN configuration within the WiFi data model.

methods.name: Lanconfig_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets the value of a specified string parameter related to LAN configuration within the WiFi data model.
